<template>
</template>

<script>

export default {
  name: 'App',
  data() {
    return {
      username: "",
      password: "",
    }
  },
  methods: {

    Login() {
      let realEmployeeData = JSON.parse(localStorage.employee);
      let realAdminData = JSON.parse(localStorage.admin);
      
      if (this.username == realEmployeeData.username && this.password == realEmployeeData.password){
        console.log('employee logged in');
      }
      else if (this.username == realAdminData.username && this.password == realAdminData.password){
        console.log('admin logged in');
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
    .password {
      background: url('./assets/lock.svg') no-repeat;
      background-position: right 5px bottom 50%;
      padding-right: 35px;
      background-size: 25px;
    }
    .username {
      background: url('./assets/user.svg') no-repeat;
      background-position: right 10px bottom 50%;
      padding-right: 40px;
      background-size: 20px;
    }
    @media (min-width: 0px) {
      .box {
        width: 86%;
      }
      .line {
        display: none;
      }
      .box-header {
        color: black;
        background-color: none;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
    }
    @media (min-width: 576px) {
      .box {
        width: 400px;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.25);
      }
      .line {
        display: block;
      }
      .box-header {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: rgb(25, 135, 85);
        padding: 20px; color:white;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    }

    .box {
        margin: auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    img {
      width: 200px;
    }


    .input-with-label input {
      color: #6C757D;
    }
    .input-with-label label {
      margin-right: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
</style>
